  <brief_title>Position of EGD in Droplet Spreading</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Comparison of Left Lateral Versus Prone Position in Saliva Droplet Spreading During Upper Gastrointestinal Endoscopy; a Pilot Study of Randomized Trial</official_title>
